1
00:01:41,090 --> 00:01:45,990
[Justifiable Defense]

2
00:01:46,030 --> 00:01:48,970
[Episode 10]

3
00:01:53,479 --> 00:01:54,920
By the time I am released,

4
00:01:56,759 --> 00:01:58,560
the rainy season should be over.

5
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:05,790
You won't hire a lawyer?

6
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:08,740
You plan to get out of here on your own?

7
00:02:09,910 --> 00:02:12,000
I can defend myself at the hearing.

8
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:13,560
Defend yourself?

9
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,680
You're locked up in here every day.

10
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:17,340
How will you defend yourself?

11
00:02:21,190 --> 00:02:22,520
Locked up in here,

12
00:02:23,030 --> 00:02:25,590
I don't know what's happening
in the outside world.

13
00:02:25,590 --> 00:02:27,190
But there is someone who will

14
00:02:27,190 --> 00:02:29,190
bring me information from outside.

15
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:35,000
Me?

16
00:02:35,450 --> 00:02:37,120
I rearrange and analyze

17
00:02:37,750 --> 00:02:39,350
the information you bring me

18
00:02:40,079 --> 00:02:42,010
to find potential possibilities.

19
00:02:44,079 --> 00:02:44,880
Write it down.

20
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:51,370
So what possibilities have you found?

21
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:53,780
The human eye is very sensitive to light.

22
00:02:55,590 --> 00:02:56,910
Mei Zheng once said

23
00:02:57,310 --> 00:02:59,120
she witnessed the entire crime,

24
00:03:00,300 --> 00:03:03,380
using a beam of light to distinguish
between two knives.

25
00:03:03,380 --> 00:03:05,190
But in Jiang Ting's testimony,

26
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:07,610
there was no mention of this light.

27
00:03:07,990 --> 00:03:09,560
So there are two possibilities.

28
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:10,310
First,

29
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:12,610
Mei Zheng didn't use a flashlight.

30
00:03:12,750 --> 00:03:13,520
Second,

31
00:03:14,030 --> 00:03:16,340
she never witnessed the murder at all.

32
00:03:16,540 --> 00:03:17,400
Mei Zheng anticipated

33
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:20,200
that Zhang Yuan would eventually
find Jiang Ting.

34
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:22,120
She only needed to keep fueling

35
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:24,579
the flames of revenge
in Jiang Ting's heart.

36
00:03:24,750 --> 00:03:26,150
and then watch it happen.

37
00:03:28,450 --> 00:03:30,220
When Jiang Ting committed the murder,

38
00:03:30,220 --> 00:03:31,470
she came out and testified

39
00:03:31,470 --> 00:03:33,210
that her actions were justifiable defense.

40
00:03:33,210 --> 00:03:34,680
Then a perfect revenge was finished.

41
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:37,340
There's just one thing I'm still
not sure about.

42
00:03:37,750 --> 00:03:40,360
Did Mei Zheng just want to have
Zhang Yuan killed for revenge

43
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:41,820
or did she also plan to send

44
00:03:42,190 --> 00:03:44,250
Jiang Ting to prison at the same time?

45
00:03:45,079 --> 00:03:47,010
No matter which possibility it is,

46
00:03:47,910 --> 00:03:49,120
the most crucial evidence now

47
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,520
should be with Mei Zheng.

48
00:04:02,030 --> 00:04:03,960
Are the handcuffs uncomfortable?

49
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:05,880
I've never had the chance before

50
00:04:06,710 --> 00:04:08,710
to examine handcuffs so carefully.

51
00:04:08,710 --> 00:04:10,590
There are three metal rings in the middle,

52
00:04:10,590 --> 00:04:12,520
connecting the cuffs on both sides

53
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:14,530
and restraining a person here.

54
00:04:17,140 --> 00:04:20,000
If the two ends of the handcuffs
represent Li Mufeng

55
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:21,070
and Jiang Ting,

56
00:04:22,270 --> 00:04:25,000
then the metal ring connecting them
in the middle

57
00:04:25,270 --> 00:04:26,240
is Mei Zheng.

58
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:55,190
Deputy Chief Prosecutor Fang,

59
00:04:55,190 --> 00:04:56,990
would you like hot or cold water?

60
00:04:57,270 --> 00:04:58,470
Hot water, thank you.

61
00:05:02,750 --> 00:05:05,210
Is this where you saw
into Jiang Ting's home?

62
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:16,870
Thank you.

63
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:29,830
Zheng.

64
00:05:31,750 --> 00:05:34,430
You seem quite nervous every time
you see me.

65
00:05:42,390 --> 00:05:43,800
May I ask why?

66
00:05:44,510 --> 00:05:45,750
You seem to have no problem

67
00:05:45,750 --> 00:05:47,350
communicating with others.

68
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:51,310
Because they're just ordinary people,

69
00:05:51,310 --> 00:05:53,240
but you're here to interrogate me.

70
00:05:57,370 --> 00:05:59,630
So how do you communicate with Li Mufeng?

71
00:06:03,010 --> 00:06:04,010
With Jiang Ting?

72
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:06,890
And with Duan Hongshan?

73
00:06:08,190 --> 00:06:09,270
Or do you just

74
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:11,530
tell people what they want to hear?

75
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:16,430
You're joking around.

76
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,390
Is that funny?

77
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:22,130
I never joke during an interrogation.

78
00:06:27,870 --> 00:06:30,120
Actually, before you took over this case,

79
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:32,360
I had some contact with a prosecutors.

80
00:06:33,310 --> 00:06:34,800
I know, Director Duan.

81
00:06:35,430 --> 00:06:37,230
But he's a suspect now,

82
00:06:37,370 --> 00:06:38,430
so I need you to

83
00:06:38,430 --> 00:06:39,600
explain your relationship with Jiang Ting

84
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:40,830
to me again.

85
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:41,720
Okay.

86
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:45,040
We were schoolmates in high school.

87
00:06:45,390 --> 00:06:46,120
So was I.

88
00:06:46,750 --> 00:06:48,210
She was even my classmate.

89
00:06:48,630 --> 00:06:50,630
But I wouldn't go to her home to cook.

90
00:06:51,670 --> 00:06:52,630
Neither would I.

91
00:06:52,630 --> 00:06:54,000
Really? You wouldn't?

92
00:07:06,860 --> 00:07:08,190
Did you get to know about

93
00:07:08,190 --> 00:07:10,050
Jiang Ting's situation long ago?

94
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:13,000
All her neighbors knew.

95
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:14,560
But they surely didn't know
about the past

96
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:16,890
of you, Jiang Ting, and Zhang Yuan, right?

97
00:07:22,270 --> 00:07:23,260
Well.

98
00:07:23,410 --> 00:07:25,430
Just because he was Jiang Ting's husband,

99
00:07:25,430 --> 00:07:27,390
my contact with her made me an accomplice,

100
00:07:27,390 --> 00:07:28,310
and everything I did

101
00:07:28,310 --> 00:07:30,040
was taking revenge?

102
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:33,070
I don't mean that.

103
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:52,680
Zheng.

104
00:07:55,750 --> 00:07:56,800
I know that

105
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:59,120
the past 14 years

106
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:01,850
must have been really hard for you.

107
00:08:05,270 --> 00:08:06,270
It's time for you

108
00:08:07,310 --> 00:08:09,190
to come up from underwater,

109
00:08:09,830 --> 00:08:11,120
take a good breath,

110
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:13,120
and look at yourself.

111
00:08:18,070 --> 00:08:20,200
Many people went through misfortunes

112
00:08:20,390 --> 00:08:21,480
as they grew up.

113
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:23,760
I had those experiences too.

114
00:08:25,830 --> 00:08:28,020
So I understand your reluctance
to move forward.

115
00:08:28,020 --> 00:08:28,560
[Mei Zheng is a slut who caused my son's
death and I'll never forgive you.]

116
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:29,690
You can't get over it

117
00:08:30,350 --> 00:08:31,750
and you feel dead inside.

118
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:33,789
It seems as if there were only two ways

119
00:08:33,789 --> 00:08:34,870
that could save us.

120
00:08:35,549 --> 00:08:36,630
The first is

121
00:08:36,750 --> 00:08:37,360
to get back what was lost.

122
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:37,870
[Petitioner] [Witness]

123
00:08:37,870 --> 00:08:39,630
I just want to tell the truth.

124
00:08:39,900 --> 00:08:40,669
The second

125
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:43,309
is to destroy what we hate.

126
00:08:47,020 --> 00:08:48,520
Do you feel so?

127
00:08:52,910 --> 00:08:54,910
I also rose from misfortune before.

128
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:56,870
So,

129
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:58,790
I want to tell you,

130
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:02,020
maybe there's a third choice for you.

131
00:09:04,030 --> 00:09:05,490
Have you thought about it?

132
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:08,790
We only live once.

133
00:09:09,390 --> 00:09:11,650
We can't be troubled by the past forever.

134
00:09:25,030 --> 00:09:25,790
Zheng.

135
00:09:26,870 --> 00:09:27,930
What you're trying

136
00:09:28,590 --> 00:09:30,850
to get back now is dangerous.

137
00:09:31,420 --> 00:09:32,950
I can't do nothing about it.

138
00:09:33,430 --> 00:09:35,090
What you're trying to cover up

139
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:37,440
is exactly what I'm good at uncovering.

140
00:09:38,570 --> 00:09:39,840
Please, you have to believe me.

141
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:40,870
What I'm telling you

142
00:09:40,870 --> 00:09:42,670
is not my baseless speculation.

143
00:09:43,550 --> 00:09:44,720
I ask you again.

144
00:09:48,390 --> 00:09:50,520
Were you and Jiang Ting conspirators?

145
00:09:53,870 --> 00:09:55,530
You made so many dishes for me,

146
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:57,240
yet you're leaving.

147
00:09:57,810 --> 00:09:58,940
The kid is asleep?

148
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:08,240
Don't worry too much.

149
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:09,810
If anything unexpected happens,

150
00:10:09,810 --> 00:10:11,260
call me immediately.

151
00:10:11,390 --> 00:10:13,510
I'll come by more these days.

152
00:10:19,560 --> 00:10:20,590
How about this?

153
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:23,140
I'll install a camera across the way

154
00:10:23,140 --> 00:10:24,630
to record everything constantly.

155
00:10:24,630 --> 00:10:26,530
That way, we'll have evidence.

156
00:10:26,560 --> 00:10:27,790
If he really comes

157
00:10:27,790 --> 00:10:28,670
and hurt you,

158
00:10:29,070 --> 00:10:31,000
we'll give the video to the police.

159
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:32,470
You can report him for domestic violence,

160
00:10:32,470 --> 00:10:34,600
and he'll have to agree to divorce you.

161
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:44,790
I just wanted to help her.

162
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:48,360
Help her kill Zhang Yuan?

163
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:50,870
I...

164
00:10:51,270 --> 00:10:53,330
I wanted her to have a different life.

165
00:10:58,910 --> 00:11:00,670
So all of this was your plan.

166
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:02,670
I...

167
00:11:03,790 --> 00:11:04,600
I don't know.

168
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:06,790
I didn't expect things would
turn out like this.

169
00:11:06,790 --> 00:11:08,390
I just wanted to help her break free.

170
00:11:08,390 --> 00:11:10,440
So what was your expectation?

171
00:11:10,460 --> 00:11:12,430
Or what was your plan?

172
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:17,200
We anticipated

173
00:11:19,390 --> 00:11:22,050
Zhang Yuan would come after her
sooner or later.

174
00:11:23,480 --> 00:11:25,600
But he came earlier than expected.

175
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:42,530
What could we do?

176
00:11:48,630 --> 00:11:50,390
Zhang Yuan not only came earlier

177
00:11:50,390 --> 00:11:51,940
but he also beat Jiang Ting.

178
00:11:52,270 --> 00:11:54,150
So the situation spiraled out of control.

179
00:11:54,150 --> 00:11:56,320
Jiang Ting had no choice but to
grab a knife and fight back,

180
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:58,240
stabbing Zhang Yuan seven times in a row.

181
00:11:58,240 --> 00:11:59,030
At that time,

182
00:11:59,390 --> 00:12:01,000
your plan had to change.

183
00:12:01,030 --> 00:12:01,960
Right?

184
00:12:07,360 --> 00:12:08,560
We didn't have a plan.

185
00:12:14,270 --> 00:12:15,670
And you have no evidence.

186
00:12:22,790 --> 00:12:23,600
Zheng.

187
00:12:28,890 --> 00:12:30,950
When I said I understand how you felt,

188
00:12:31,510 --> 00:12:32,360
I meant it.

189
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:35,720
I genuinely want to help you.

190
00:12:36,080 --> 00:12:37,200
But the premise is

191
00:12:38,960 --> 00:12:41,290
that you must be willing to save yourself.

192
00:12:55,270 --> 00:12:58,800
What you did for Jiang Ting was
returning kindness for cruelty.

193
00:13:05,120 --> 00:13:06,910
You've done so much for her.

194
00:13:07,670 --> 00:13:09,480
I'm truly impressed.

195
00:13:13,120 --> 00:13:15,120
I just feel so much sympathy for her.

196
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:19,480
And this time,

197
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:23,840
her actions were indeed
justifiable defense.

198
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:30,400
What about the evidence?

199
00:13:31,160 --> 00:13:33,220
Can you give me the evidence now?

200
00:13:45,150 --> 00:13:45,840
Fang.

201
00:13:46,240 --> 00:13:47,760
Since Mei Zheng has the video,

202
00:13:47,760 --> 00:13:49,590
why didn't she hand it earlier?

203
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:52,080
If you had been her

204
00:13:52,240 --> 00:13:54,570
who had recorded a video that's so blurry,

205
00:13:55,600 --> 00:13:57,200
would you have submitted it?

206
00:14:22,860 --> 00:14:23,530
The light!

207
00:14:25,150 --> 00:14:26,150
Can you please

208
00:14:26,170 --> 00:14:27,810
stay calm?

209
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:28,440
You scared me.

210
00:14:28,440 --> 00:14:29,270
I'm sorry.

211
00:14:29,510 --> 00:14:32,470
That beam of light Mei Zheng mentioned
really isn't there.

212
00:14:32,470 --> 00:14:33,200
So,

213
00:14:34,790 --> 00:14:36,960
Duan Hongshan's inference was correct.

214
00:14:36,960 --> 00:14:39,290
Though Mei Zheng didn't admit it herself,

215
00:14:39,720 --> 00:14:42,200
I think she most likely committed perjury.

216
00:14:42,670 --> 00:14:43,670
No wonder

217
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:45,600
she specifically pointed out

218
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:47,270
Zhang Yuan at the hearing,

219
00:14:47,960 --> 00:14:48,600
right?

220
00:14:49,770 --> 00:14:52,030
Mei Zheng had already set everything up,

221
00:14:52,360 --> 00:14:53,320
but things didn't

222
00:14:53,320 --> 00:14:54,840
go as she had planned.

223
00:14:55,390 --> 00:14:56,390
In that case,

224
00:14:56,390 --> 00:14:59,520
what Mei Zheng did constitutes
preparation for a crime.

225
00:15:02,600 --> 00:15:03,910
But if the crime

226
00:15:03,910 --> 00:15:06,010
remained at the preparation stage,

227
00:15:06,510 --> 00:15:08,960
and Mei Zheng had the motive
to kill Zhang Yuan,

228
00:15:08,960 --> 00:15:10,390
but due to unexpected circumstances,

229
00:15:10,390 --> 00:15:11,790
the action was terminated,

230
00:15:11,790 --> 00:15:13,320
and the objective evidence

231
00:15:14,630 --> 00:15:16,490
shows that a new danger appeared,

232
00:15:18,570 --> 00:15:21,910
then how should we determine the nature
of Jiang Ting's actions?

233
00:15:21,910 --> 00:15:24,080
There was an unplanned real danger.

234
00:15:24,080 --> 00:15:26,740
How should Jiang Ting's actions
be determined?

235
00:15:45,720 --> 00:15:46,790
That's me?

236
00:15:47,720 --> 00:15:48,440
It's you,

237
00:15:48,720 --> 00:15:49,550
your home,

238
00:15:49,630 --> 00:15:50,600
your balcony,

239
00:15:50,600 --> 00:15:52,200
and your husband Zhang Yuan.

240
00:15:52,550 --> 00:15:54,510
After stabbing him the first time,

241
00:15:54,510 --> 00:15:56,120
you stabbed him six more times,

242
00:15:56,120 --> 00:15:57,200
and he died.

243
00:15:58,120 --> 00:15:59,320
It's so blurry,

244
00:15:59,910 --> 00:16:01,370
How can you be sure it's me?

245
00:16:02,120 --> 00:16:04,580
Then let's wait for the video
to be restored.

246
00:16:08,870 --> 00:16:10,200
It can be restored?

247
00:16:11,720 --> 00:16:12,870
Once it's restored,

248
00:16:13,120 --> 00:16:14,450
take a closer look at it.

249
00:16:15,240 --> 00:16:16,970
Look carefully and you'll know

250
00:16:17,150 --> 00:16:18,550
my actions were indeed
justifiable defense.

251
00:16:18,550 --> 00:16:20,010
I will watch it carefully.

252
00:16:20,080 --> 00:16:21,670
whether your actions were
justifiable defense

253
00:16:21,670 --> 00:16:23,070
isn't up to you to decide.

254
00:16:23,240 --> 00:16:25,170
We only base our judgment on facts.

255
00:16:35,600 --> 00:16:37,000
Fourteen years ago,

256
00:16:38,150 --> 00:16:39,550
I was your class monitor.

257
00:16:42,320 --> 00:16:43,720
Now,

258
00:16:46,550 --> 00:16:48,630
you're the prosecutor judging me.

259
00:16:50,510 --> 00:16:51,750
I can't judge you.

260
00:16:52,480 --> 00:16:54,610
I can only characterize your actions.

261
00:16:56,150 --> 00:16:57,350
My characterization

262
00:16:57,840 --> 00:16:59,000
is based on truth.

263
00:17:00,600 --> 00:17:01,440
So,

264
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:04,000
I hope you will tell me

265
00:17:04,310 --> 00:17:06,569
everything you know in complete detail.

266
00:17:07,920 --> 00:17:09,030
I can't save you.

267
00:17:10,720 --> 00:17:12,589
Only you can save yourself.

268
00:17:14,589 --> 00:17:15,990
Am I making myself clear?

269
00:17:26,160 --> 00:17:28,560
That woman who should have been my enemy...

270
00:17:29,910 --> 00:17:31,020
It was she

271
00:17:32,300 --> 00:17:34,540
who pulled me out of the abyss.

272
00:17:51,520 --> 00:17:54,740
[Qianhu Avenue, Xinhu West Road]

273
00:18:00,910 --> 00:18:04,640
[Qianhu Avenue, Xinhu West Road]

274
00:18:04,640 --> 00:18:06,440
I met you at the aquarium.

275
00:18:08,180 --> 00:18:09,460
You swam really well.

276
00:18:16,110 --> 00:18:17,240
I work there

277
00:18:17,240 --> 00:18:18,270
thanks to you.

278
00:18:29,960 --> 00:18:31,690
You can't hold a baby like that,

279
00:18:32,350 --> 00:18:34,210
If you keep covering him this way,

280
00:18:34,310 --> 00:18:35,400
he'll suffocate.

281
00:18:45,860 --> 00:18:47,060
Which bus do you take?

282
00:18:50,200 --> 00:18:51,240
Route 28.

283
00:18:53,790 --> 00:18:54,510
Go home.

