Hurry up.

569
00:32:08,640 --> 00:32:09,350
Hurry up.

570
00:32:11,240 --> 00:32:11,920
Put it on.

571
00:32:13,330 --> 00:32:14,930
You don’t need to wear a coat.

572
00:32:15,350 --> 00:32:17,350
Stop making excuses and take it off.

573
00:32:19,590 --> 00:32:21,070
That's Director Chen
from the Education Bureau.

574
00:32:21,070 --> 00:32:22,620
Don't embarrass me.

575
00:32:27,740 --> 00:32:29,270
Go ahead and eat if you want.

576
00:32:32,200 --> 00:32:33,060
Help yourself.

577
00:33:41,950 --> 00:33:43,100
Turn on the AC.

578
00:33:43,550 --> 00:33:44,200
Okay,

579
00:33:44,220 --> 00:33:45,750
I've turned on the AC for you

580
00:33:45,750 --> 00:33:47,880
and set it to the optimal temperature.

581
00:34:35,400 --> 00:34:37,800
Why didn't you tell me
you were coming back?

582
00:34:39,000 --> 00:34:40,330
What are you doing here?

583
00:34:42,360 --> 00:34:44,190
I only heard from the procuratorate

584
00:34:44,190 --> 00:34:46,190
that you were being released today.

585
00:34:46,190 --> 00:34:48,000
So I came over to tidy up for you.

586
00:34:49,280 --> 00:34:50,889
I took all your dirty clothes

587
00:34:51,070 --> 00:34:52,630
to the dry cleaner's.

588
00:34:53,280 --> 00:34:54,880
And I threw out a lot of those messy shoes

589
00:34:54,880 --> 00:34:56,000
lying on the floor.

590
00:34:56,960 --> 00:34:58,510
You live here for now.

591
00:34:58,510 --> 00:35:00,110
Don't buy anything useless.

592
00:35:00,880 --> 00:35:03,150
Once the gossip dies down,

593
00:35:03,150 --> 00:35:04,410
you can move back home.

594
00:35:06,000 --> 00:35:07,070
I'm not going back.

595
00:35:08,110 --> 00:35:09,280
Don't worry,

596
00:35:10,510 --> 00:35:12,370
I'm never going back there again.

597
00:35:15,710 --> 00:35:16,880
What do you mean?

598
00:35:24,230 --> 00:35:25,630
Let me ask you something.

599
00:35:27,000 --> 00:35:29,190
I was locked up for so long.

600
00:35:32,800 --> 00:35:34,660
Why didn't you visit me even once?

601
00:35:36,110 --> 00:35:37,480
How dare you blame me?

602
00:35:39,760 --> 00:35:42,360
I've been a successful lady
for my entire life.

603
00:35:42,840 --> 00:35:44,630
The daughter I was always so proud of

604
00:35:44,630 --> 00:35:46,150
killed someone.

605
00:35:46,840 --> 00:35:47,960
Do you know how many people at work

606
00:35:47,960 --> 00:35:50,670
are laughing at me behind my back now?

607
00:35:51,110 --> 00:35:52,320
My leader today

608
00:35:52,440 --> 00:35:54,280
told me to take time off

609
00:35:54,280 --> 00:35:55,480
to lay low for a while.

610
00:35:56,280 --> 00:35:57,880
Don't think you're the only one...

611
00:35:57,880 --> 00:35:58,710
Just go.

612
00:36:02,400 --> 00:36:03,670
You're kicking me out?

613
00:36:04,760 --> 00:36:05,630
Jiang Ting.

614
00:36:05,920 --> 00:36:08,630
I raised you all by myself
with such hardship.

615
00:36:08,630 --> 00:36:10,000
Rain or shine,

616
00:36:10,000 --> 00:36:11,800
I took you to dance lessons.

617
00:36:12,110 --> 00:36:12,960
Don't think

618
00:36:12,960 --> 00:36:15,080
you're the only victim here.

619
00:36:15,920 --> 00:36:17,880
How dare you throw my bag!

620
00:36:17,900 --> 00:36:18,820
Jiang Ting.

621
00:36:19,150 --> 00:36:20,030
Jiang Ting,

622
00:36:20,030 --> 00:36:21,800
Open this door!

623
00:36:22,440 --> 00:36:26,110
You ungrateful daughter!

624
00:36:26,800 --> 00:36:29,000
I raise your child all by myself!

625
00:36:29,590 --> 00:36:30,960
Open the door!

626
00:37:56,760 --> 00:37:57,920
Finally free.

627
00:38:01,230 --> 00:38:02,400
I'm free,

628
00:38:03,150 --> 00:38:04,680
but it doesn't feel like it.

629
00:38:07,280 --> 00:38:09,190
I always owe you something to say.

630
00:38:13,110 --> 00:38:14,670
And I owe her it too.

631
00:38:21,110 --> 00:38:22,280
I'm sorry!

632
00:38:23,070 --> 00:38:24,670
I'm sorry.

633
00:38:26,440 --> 00:38:27,400
I'm sorry.

634
00:38:28,190 --> 00:38:29,070
I'm sorry.

635
00:38:37,500 --> 00:38:42,970
♪ The morning breeze blows away worries ♪

636
00:38:44,690 --> 00:38:49,940
♪ Beyond the window waits a cliff ♪

637
00:38:51,610 --> 00:38:53,030
♪ Crossing roads,
finding freedom in the fall ♪

638
00:38:53,030 --> 00:38:55,250
Everything happened so fast,

639
00:38:56,030 --> 00:38:57,660
like a dream.

640
00:38:58,450 --> 00:38:58,730
It's all over now.

641
00:38:58,730 --> 00:39:04,320
♪ About the dialogue of fate,
I can't tell what I feel ♪

642
00:39:04,320 --> 00:39:05,400
It's all over now.

643
00:39:06,100 --> 00:39:11,790
♪ Wandering alone and silently at night ♪

644
00:39:12,840 --> 00:39:18,710
♪ Kind and stubborn, we stick together
in the bumpy life journey ♪

645
00:39:19,770 --> 00:39:25,820
♪ Having tasted warmth and cold,
identity swirls like a vortex ♪

646
00:39:26,970 --> 00:39:27,550
♪ Treating regrets with kindness,
yet still feeling warm ♪

647
00:39:27,550 --> 00:39:28,670
Do you know

648
00:39:30,110 --> 00:39:32,510
why I've never dared
to wear short sleeves?

649
00:39:33,820 --> 00:39:39,770
♪ No blame for the pain,
sleepless with fantasies ♪

650
00:39:40,990 --> 00:39:45,180
♪ Letting go with a smile,
still drifting along ♪

651
00:39:45,180 --> 00:39:45,980
Here.

652
00:39:47,820 --> 00:39:51,190
♪ The light and shadow of fate
keeps asking about living ♪

653
00:39:51,190 --> 00:39:52,510
Scream. Go ahead, scream.

654
00:39:52,510 --> 00:39:53,440
And here.

655
00:39:55,100 --> 00:39:56,670
♪ Staggering along the way ♪

656
00:39:56,670 --> 00:39:57,550
And here.

657
00:39:57,550 --> 00:39:57,880
-Stop.
-Look.

658
00:39:57,880 --> 00:39:58,190
♪ There's a soul warm and comforting ♪

659
00:39:58,190 --> 00:39:59,440
-Stop.
-Look!

660
00:39:59,440 --> 00:40:00,760
-All right.
-Stop.

661
00:40:01,030 --> 00:40:01,890
Okay, stop it.

662
00:40:01,890 --> 00:40:07,670
♪ If I can see the answer before sunset ♪

663
00:40:07,670 --> 00:40:08,840
It's okay now.

664
00:40:09,300 --> 00:40:15,370
♪ In this storm, we'll be safe ♪

665
00:40:17,030 --> 00:40:19,280
I made the mistakes over a decade ago.

666
00:40:20,510 --> 00:40:22,510
I wasn't mature back then.

667
00:40:24,280 --> 00:40:25,480
I made mistakes.

668
00:40:28,670 --> 00:40:29,920
I hurt you.

669
00:40:33,030 --> 00:40:34,110
and hurt

670
00:40:34,800 --> 00:40:35,400
her.

671
00:40:37,840 --> 00:40:39,190
I married Zhang Yuan.

672
00:40:39,920 --> 00:40:42,180
These ten years have been my punishment.

673
00:40:44,110 --> 00:40:45,440
I will live with guilt

674
00:40:47,670 --> 00:40:49,000
and spend my entire life

675
00:40:50,590 --> 00:40:52,400
repaying the debt I owe.

676
00:41:02,280 --> 00:41:03,230
I'm sorry,

677
00:41:05,630 --> 00:41:07,000
I'm sorry.
